She had to hold onto Quickstrike. Her legs weren't functioning 
yet. "Thanks for the help.  Could you put me back on the table. 
Coming back to life is a drag. I still don't have control of half my 
body yet. And to top it off, I can't transform." She gave a 
disspointed sigh. "I'm sorry. It's just that this isn't going as well 
as I had hoped."  She stated to shake again.  She was beginning to 
wonder if the shaking was a side affect of the liquid energon.
